# Xllopkup VS Vlookup
VLOOKUP 
Lookup Direction	Searches only vertically from top to bottom	
Column Index	Needs a column number to specify return col
Returns #N/A on no match
XLOOKUP
Can search both vertically and horizontally
Returns result based on a range for return values (no column number needed)
Can specify a custom value if not found

